---
/**
 * OriginStory Component
 *
 * Homepage snippet of the Garden City / John Mark Comer origin story.
 * Content mirrors what's on the About page — single narrative source of truth.
 */
---

<section class="section bg-warm-50">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif italic text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-8 text-primary-500 leading-tight">
        The Story Behind the Name
      </h2>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-warm-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        The name was born during land restoration — clearing invasive species with a chainsaw while listening to John Mark Comer's <em>Garden City.</em> The farm is a calling to cultivate, restore, and steward creation.
      </p>

      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-primary-400 pl-6 py-2 text-left mb-10">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-warm-600 italic leading-relaxed">
          "We're called to a very specific kind of work — to make a Garden-like world where image bearers can flourish and thrive."
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <a
        href="/about"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-semibold text-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Read Our Full Story
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
